** MobileGates Gemz API **
** Oren Shepes - 01/10 **

DESCRIPTION
-----------
This is the Gemz API. It provides REST and SOAP web services for the Gemz system.

INSTALL
-------
svn co http://oren.selfip.net/svn/mobilegates/trunk

mv APP/.htaccess.bak APP/.htaccess
mv APP/webroot/.htaccess.bak APP/webroot/.htaccess

MySQL
-----
Add user 'api_user' w/ passwd 'm0b!l3g@t3s'

DOCUMENTATION
-------------
$APP_BASE_URL/docs/api/index.html
